{"tid":355502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐盟委員會證實 有毒雞蛋輸往香港","createTime":"2017-08-11T10:41:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T01:17:05.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"384d3a73282c8e7792badb3dc9e7c492065976ca","tid":355502,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:41:17.000Z","msg":"歐洲毒雞蛋風波蔓延，歐盟委員會周五證實，毒雞蛋醜聞影響15個歐盟國家，以及香港和瑞士，輸港的有問題雞蛋分別源自比利時、荷蘭、德國及法國的農場。<br />\n<br />\n早前報道指，荷蘭有家禽場的雞蛋受有毒殺蟲劑芬普尼（fipronil）污染，荷蘭食安當局（NVWA）要下令180間農場暫停營業，官員跟進檢查後仍有138間農場停業，約佔全國業界的五分一。<br />\n芬普尼是常用除蝨藥，以治療跳蚤、蝨子和蜱蟲等，但禁止使用在家禽等動物身上，大量攝取會損害會損害腎臟、肝臟和甲狀腺。比利時被揭早在6月已知有雞蛋被芬普尼污染，但上月才通知歐盟。"},{"pid":"5ece24cd296d36b88b578376c9b1456324cab01e","tid":355502,"uid":17081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:44:22.000Z","msg":"美心仲用日本蛋實在係良心企業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b3ce8ca0c5dccc8ef8708b64f1b1274ebf3fce7","tid":355502,"uid":689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:47:08.000Z","msg":"Sauce?"},{"pid":"abc42dbfd7d38a37775863cd1f58edb3d37cfae8","tid":355502,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:52:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Sauce?</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170811/57069785\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170811%2F57069785&d=LqU%2Biehar3Y0COcM%2FKLbcEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=801c998b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170811%2F57069785&h=0ecf6ff8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170811/57069785</a>"},{"pid":"c191db7b616c5081e0dc401755efc84681416586","tid":355502,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:53:23.000Z","msg":